276
00:15:32,474 --> 00:15:34,059
Don't worry.
He's a boy scout

277
00:15:34,059 --> 00:15:35,936
and one of the best
detectives we got.

278
00:15:35,936 --> 00:15:37,813
Not only is he gonna do his job,

