335
00:19:48,939 --> 00:19:52,401
This means that they got him
and he's gonna pay, Les.

336
00:19:52,401 --> 00:19:54,611
He's gonna pay, Leslie.
I promise you.

337
00:19:54,611 --> 00:19:56,238
He's gonna pay.

338
00:20:12,546 --> 00:20:14,423
Stay right here, baby.
