354
00:21:01,303 --> 00:21:02,846
I don't know.

355
00:21:02,846 --> 00:21:04,389
I think they're trying to say

356
00:21:04,389 --> 00:21:05,766
there's something wrong
with the DNA.

357
00:21:22,574 --> 00:21:25,160
Well, apparently,
the DNA obtained

358
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:27,538
in this case
