00:21:31,375 --> 00:21:32,376
-Are you serious?
-No.

362
00:21:32,376 --> 00:21:33,836
- What is going on?
- Order in the court!

363
00:21:37,881 --> 00:21:40,259
Is there any new evidence
the state is prepared

364
00:21:40,259 --> 00:21:42,845
