00:25:19,686 --> 00:25:22,064
I, um...uh, I thought
that maybe you could--

420
00:25:22,064 --> 00:25:23,273
You thought what?

421
00:25:24,816 --> 00:25:27,444
It was an accident.
The DNA sampling.

