what he felt was right.

436
00:26:14,992 --> 00:26:16,910
Mind your freaking
business, Logan.

437
00:26:16,910 --> 00:26:21,582
I'm not
gonna say it again, Espinoza.

438
00:26:21,582 --> 00:26:24,042
Back off
or I'll make you back off.

439
00:26:30,549 --> 00:26:32,009
Oh.

440
00:26:32,009 --> 00:26:34,595
