other cops that did.

487
00:32:41,128 --> 00:32:43,839
-They were trying to--
-Retaliation?

488
00:32:43,839 --> 00:32:45,007
Yeah.

489
00:32:46,633 --> 00:32:49,303
So if I had to guess,

490
00:32:49,303 --> 00:32:52,389
this was my fault, he got away.

